node.text: BBQ never started as a way to be the best women pitmasters, that just happened… We never set out to be a pioneer. Like we’ve always said, our Dad was just trying to teach us how to make it in the world. But that doesn’t mean we don’t love supporting women in whatever their goals are. Thank you to the @kcwoso team for celebrating Juneteenth with us!!

node.title: The KC National Women's Soccer League Celebrates Juneteenth with Jones BBQ

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jones Bar-B-Q Kansas City in Jones BBQ. May be an image of 2 people, food and indoor.

node.text: The only thing that makes us smile more than our BBQ is our customers! What puts a smile on your face on a Monday? 📸: @31gapeaches⁠

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jones Bar-B-Q Kansas City on August 21, 2021. May be an image of food.

node.text: Our BBQ is so good you can’t just order one item, you just HAVE to try them all!! 😁 Tell us, which is your favorite meal off our menu 👇

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jones Bar-B-Q Kansas City on August 19, 2021. May be an image of 3 people and indoor.

node.text: We sure love to meet and hang out with our customers! Share your photos with us by tagging @jonesbbqkc in your posts and stories. 📸: @burtonkelso

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jones Bar-B-Q Kansas City on August 17, 2021. May be an image of food.

node.text:
Here at Jones, we believe in spreading the love through BBQ, but we couldn't keep our love to ourselves now could we?! That’s why our bottled sauce and rubs are available both online and in many local stores, allowing our customers to experiment and enjoy their own delicious creations from home! 📸: @alextapia45⁠
⁠

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jones Bar-B-Q Kansas City on August 14, 2021. May be an image of food.

node.text: As @zacheatskc said, “why not try it all?” We like how you think, Zach! Give our Jones Platter a taste today!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jones Bar-B-Q Kansas City on August 11, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, food and indoor.

node.text: We love our BBQ so much, we can’t help but smile!😁

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jones Bar-B-Q Kansas City on August 09, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, food and indoor.

node.text: Sorry we can’t come to the phone right now, we’re busy slicin’ some of the best BBQ in KC!

node.text: Don’t forget, we’ll be back to our normal hours starting Tuesday, August 10! Catch us smoking up all the meats from 11 AM to 3 PM… ish.⁠

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jones Bar-B-Q Kansas City on August 05, 2021. May be an image of food and indoor.

node.text: We wanna see how you use the best BBQ sauce in town!! Tag us @jonesbbqkc to be featured.

node.text: Oops, we didn’t mean to make you drool! It’s just a natural side-effect of our scrumptious plates. 🤤⁠

node.text: Feeling sauce-y? Good thing, we’ve got lots. Tell us, what’s your go-to: sweet and tangy or hot and spicy! 👇

node.text: While we love to cook and smoke our meats, we don't love to cook ourselves in this HOT HEAT! 🔥That being said, we will be CLOSED today, July 29th due to extreme temperatures. No fear though, our vending machine is stocked with your favorites. Thank you for understanding ❤️
